OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FFormer boxing world champion Ricky
OL,7,FHatton had made plans he was looking
OL,8,Fforward to and it was not clear he
OL,9,Fintended to take his own life, an
OL,10,Finquest has found.
OL,12,FThe 46-year-old, described as a doting
OL,13,Ffather, was found dead at his at home
OL,14,Fin Hyde, Greater Manchester on Sunday
OL,15,F14, September.
OL,17,FAn inquest into his death heard the
OL,18,Fformer boxer, known to fans as "The
OL,19,FHitman", was in good spirits and,
OL,20,Fdespite past troubles with alcohol and
OL,21,Fdrugs, had been the best "in years".
OL,26,@}D@ZOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
