FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FHe had taken his daughters and
OL,7,Fgranddaughter out to a pub for a meal
OL,8,Fon the evening of Friday 12 September,
OL,9,Fappearing "normal", Stockport
OL,10,FCoroner's Court heard.
OL,12,FAfter dropping them off he told them
OL,13,Fhe would see them in a couple of days
OL,14,Fafter a trip to Dubai where he was due
OL,15,Fto promote an exhibition boxing match,
OL,16,Fbut concerns were raised the following
OL,17,Fday when he failed to attend a
OL,18,Fscheduled event.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
