OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FAt 6.30am on Sunday, his manager, Paul
OL,7,FSpeak, arrived at Hatton's home in
OL,8,FHyde, Tameside, to collect him for a
OL,9,Fflight to Dubai where he found the
OL,10,Fformer champion unresponsive in an
OL,11,Fupstairs game room.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Hatton's son Campbell
OL,14,Ftold the inquest he did not believe
OL,15,Fhis dad's death had been premeditated,
OL,16,Fadding while he had been open about
OL,17,Fhis mental health and drug use, he had
OL,18,Fbeen in "the best place he had been in
OL,19,Ffor years".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,F"He lived life - in and out of the
OL,7,Fring - at 110% and always said he
OL,8,Fnever regretted it," Campbell said.
OL,10,F"He was always generous with people.
OL,11,FHe was always extremely well loved and
OL,12,Fcherished by all of us."
OL,14,FHe added: "We felt he was in the best
OL,15,Fplace he had been in recent years.
OL,17,F"The family believe he was the best he
OL,18,Fhad been in years and made massive
OL,19,Fplans for the future which leads us to
OL,20,Fbelieve this was not premeditated."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@XO]vD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
