PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FTests showed the proud Mancunian and
OL,7,Flifelong Manchester City fan was "well
OL,8,Fover" the drink-drive limit at the
OL,9,Ftime of his death. Traces of previous
OL,10,Fuse of cocaine and cannabis were also
OL,11,Ffound.
OL,13,FPost-mortem evidence also showed some
OL,14,Fdamage to his brain identified as
OL,15,Fchronic traumatic encephalopathy
OL,16,F(CTE), caused by repeated head
OL,17,Finjuries commonly found in contact
OL,18,Fsports.
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FAn expert told the inquest it was rare
OL,7,Fto find in someone of his age, and was
OL,8,Fusually only found in older people
OL,9,Fwith Alzheimers.
OL,11,FIt can cause behavioural and mood
OL,12,Fchanges, as well as memory loss, but
OL,13,Fit was not possible to ascertain if
OL,14,Fthis affected his behaviour, the
OL,15,Finquest heard.
OL,17,FCampbell told the inquest there had
OL,18,Fbeen a "decline" in his father's short-
OL,19,Fterm memory often forgetting
OL,20,Fconversations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,F"Over the last two or three years we
OL,7,Fall noticed a significant decline in
OL,8,Fhis short-term memory," he said.
OL,10,F"He repeated himself constantly, had
OL,11,Fto write things down and had to be
OL,12,Freminded about things he had to do day
OL,13,Fto day."
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
