OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FAlison Mutch, senior coroner for South
OL,7,FManchester, told the court, attended
OL,8,Fby the boxer's father, brother, son
OL,9,Fand ex-partner and mother of his
OL,10,Fdaughters, that no notes had been
OL,11,Ffound from Hatton and there was no
OL,12,Finformation uncovered by police to
OL,13,Fsuggest he was planning to take his
OL,14,Fown life.
OL,16,FConcluding the inquest, she said: "He
OL,17,Fhad made significant future plans and
OL,18,Fno notes were found indicating he
OL,19,Fintended to take his own life.
OL,26,@xD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,F"I have listened very carefully to all
OL,7,Fthe evidence. When I add everything
OL,8,Ftogether, I cannot be satisfied he
OL,9,Fintended to take his own life.
OL,11,F"Therefore, it is not possible in law
OL,12,Ffor me to conclude suicide. I have
OL,13,Fconcluded a narrative verdict.
OL,15,F"His intention remains unclear as he
OL,16,Fwas under the influence of alcohol and
OL,17,Fthe neuropathological post-mortem
OL,18,Ffound evidence of chronic traumatic
OL,19,Fencephalopathy and that's the
OL,20,Fconclusion I draw."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
