FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FCampbell broke down in tears at the
OL,7,Fconclusion of the inquest and was
OL,8,Fhugged by his grandfather, Ray Hatton,
OL,9,F75.
OL,11,FJennifer Dooley, mother of his
OL,12,Fdaughters, Millie, 13, Fearne, 12, and
OL,13,Fwho was Hatton's partner for 11 years
OL,14,Funtil 2016, said he was a very hands-
OL,15,Fon father who doted on his children,
OL,16,Fand they all continued to spend time
OL,17,Ftogether after the split.
OL,19,F"He often said that the time he spent
OL,20,Fwith his daughter was when he was
OL,21,Fhappiest," she said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
