FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FHatton took his daughters and
OL,7,Fgranddaughter, Lyla, for dinner at a
OL,8,Flocal pub on the Friday night before
OL,9,Fhis death.
OL,11,FWhen he said goodbye, he told them he
OL,12,Fwould see them in a couple of days on
OL,13,Fhis return from Dubai, the inquest
OL,14,Fheard.
OL,16,FDetective Sergeant Helen Grigalis,
OL,17,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police, told
OL,18,Fthe hearing Hatton returned home after
OL,19,Fthe meal at around 7.55pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
