PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774210270
OL,3,C'Not clear that Ricky Hatton intended
OL,4,Cto take his own life', coroner finds
OL,6,FHe sent a message to a friend at
OL,7,F8.05pm and his phone last unlocked at
OL,8,F12.02am early on Saturday September
OL,9,F13, with no further use after that
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
